text: Ahmad Subagja Baasith (born June 15, 1996) is an Indonesian professional footballer who plays as a defensive midfielder for Liga 2 club PSIM Yogyakarta. ==Career== ===Persib Bandung=== Baasith made his professional debut in the Liga 1 on April 22, 2017 against PS TNI.Pertandingan PS TNI vs Persib Bandung 22 April 2017 liga-indonesia.id. April 22, 2017 ===Persela Lamongan=== He joined Persela Lamongan in January 2018. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1996 births Category:Sportspeople from Bandung Category:Indonesian footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Liga 1 (Indonesia) players Category:Persib Bandung players Category:Persela Lamongan players
